Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance

Reference: - Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance, Government Decision No. BCH-2025 / Q.98 / Constructions,
Government of Backward Classes and Mostly Backward Girls under Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance

The hostel building, Alibag, G. Raigad, was constructed at a cost of Rs. 857.89 Attention / - Government decision regarding construction budget of such amount. Subject to the Articles prescribed under the 10.10.2025, Administrative approval is granted and the Government Decision includes the following Conditions No. (lu): -
(l) The operational mechanism for the present construction will be Maharashtra-State Infrastructure Development Corporation (MSIDC), Mumbai.
(2) The other provisions of the Government Decision shall remain in force.
The Government Corrigendum is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
